{
  "stem": "21626.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But of course, that experience made me realize that the occupation was not a game and made me fear what else it might mean.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And moreover, it made Mother realize that we were in danger.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And after that, she left no stone unturned looking for a way to send me and my sister somewhere to safety.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I know our parents talked about possibly leaving the country.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But it was difficult for them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They didn't have that many contacts.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But moreover, Mother just felt she could not leave her blind mother behind.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And so they thought at least we should go to safety.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "My father was an optimist anyway.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "You know, he, he thought whatever might happen, it would be a-- if a war did come, it would be a storm in a teacup.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And, and nobody really [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] had an inkling what terrible fate Hitler had in store for the Jews, not, not then, not in Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Then my mother heard that there was a possibility of Jewish children coming to Britain on children transports.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And she went to Prague and found out all about it, actually through Aunt Marta and through Aunt, Aunt, Aunt, Aunt-- through Uncle Gustav, who put the names of their sons down on this-- for the transports.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I had no idea.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "All I knew was that she had our photographs, my sister's and mine, professionally taken.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we didn't note for what purpose this was.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We thought it was just for the family album.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] My father didn't know, either, not until-- when was it?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It must have been [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] April, May, I think, May 1939.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We were sitting at the table having dinner.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And my mother's plate remained untouched.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
